ShouldersFixedBar.name: Fixed Bar Side Deltoid Stretch
ShouldersFixedBar.preparation: Face stationary bar. Grasp stationary bar with one hand approximately chest height. Rotate body so upper arm is positioned across chest.
ShouldersFixedBar.execution: Turn body into upper arm. Hold stretch. Repeat with opposite arm.

ShouldersSideDelt.name: Side Deltoid Stretch
ShouldersSideDelt.preparation: Position arm across chest. Place opposite hand on elbow.
ShouldersSideDelt.execution: Push elbow toward chest. Hold stretch. Repeat with opposite arm.
ShouldersSideDelt.comments: Positioning arm on upper chest stretches rear deltoid. See Rear Delt Stretch.
